# ğŸŒ¾ AgroSchemes - Farmer Government Aided Schemes Portal

AgroSchemes is a modern web application designed to help farmers access and apply for government-aided agricultural schemes. It provides a centralized platform to explore schemes, manage crop data, submit applications, and track application status.

